ek hi bhool ( the only mistake ) is a 1940 hindi social drama directed by vijay bhatt .   the film was produced by vijay and his brother shankar bhatt for bhatt 's production banner prakash pictures .   the music direction was by shankar rao vyas with lyrics by pandit anuj .   the film starred p. jairaj , mehtab , umakant , baby meena , prahlad dutt , rekha and baby meena ( meena kumari ) .